data.title: Most Ethereum valuation models indicate ETH is undervalued: Analyst
data.description: The native token of the Ethereum network, Ether BINANCE:ETHUSD, is undervalued in nine out of 12 commonly used valuation models, according to Ki Young Ju, a market analyst and CEO of crypto market analysis platform CryptoQuant.A composite “fair value” using all 12 valuation models prices ETH at abo…
